data.description: OUTSTANDING OPPORTUNITY!!! Here's your chance to build your dream home on 1.08 acres in one of the most desirable spots in Creve Coeur. Bring your plan, bring your builder, and bring your creativity! This level lot with mature trees will accommodate nearly whatever you'd like to create!  And you're 5 minutes from EVERYTHING! Check it out today! Property is to be sold in its current as-is condition with no warranties or representations by the Seller. Seller will not make repairs nor provide any inspections. Seller's addendum is required after terms of sale are agreed upon. Special Sale Contract (Form #2043) required. Proof of funds or pre-approval letter required with offer.
